{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tipping-content-js","path":"/ecuador","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Bars, restaurants and hotels include a 10% service charge in the bill, so tipping is not required. In the case of restaurants, it is customary to leave some spare change in reward for good service. Some restaurants that don't include the service charge will include a small piece of paper along with the bill, in which the client can specify a tip (approx. 5-10%) if they are paying with credit card.</p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/ecuador","title":"Ecuador","author":"Joni","date":"2019-11-22","image":"ecuador.jpg"}},"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5,"src":"/static/55645b80ccf9993e27c3baa52bc4f6b9/90537/ecuador.jpg","srcSet":"/static/55645b80ccf9993e27c3baa52bc4f6b9/b3ebb/ecuador.jpg 270w,\n/static/55645b80ccf9993e27c3baa52bc4f6b9/95b54/ecuador.jpg 540w,\n/static/55645b80ccf9993e27c3baa52bc4f6b9/90537/ecuador.jpg 1080w,\n/static/55645b80ccf9993e27c3baa52bc4f6b9/3cda3/ecuador.jpg 1620w,\n/static/55645b80ccf9993e27c3baa52bc4f6b9/1f682/ecuador.jpg 2160w,\n/static/55645b80ccf9993e27c3baa52bc4f6b9/2728f/ecuador.jpg 5184w","sizes":"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px"}}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"image":"ecuador.jpg"}}}